commit.message: Capitalized the first letter in the songs list for the avatar icon
Added the title edit text in the save dialog in the new song fragment
Changed the title in the EditSongFragment to be the title of the song the user selected to edit.

Added the SeekBar to change the temp when editing the music. Also, added a save menu action button to update the music after editing (for now, the only modification we can make is to change the tempo).
Added the click listener to the songs list to take the user to the EditSongFragment. This fragment only plays a songs when the user clicks on the play button on the toolbar
Fetching data from Azure in the songs fragment
Renamed mhacks.openmusic to org.mhacks.openmusic and added the midi library: com.leffi.middi
Added the EditSongFragment along with a toolbar with the corresponding menu items that are unique to this fragment: change tempo and play the song
Added a toolbar and a FramLayout to use fragments
